name: Boogie#2 Mood 2021/6.9MB
description: Mood is the 2nd digitally manipulated image of the “Boogie” gif-series and originates from StrawberryFields. Like the domino effect, this series emerges as a coherent sequence, a kind of chain reaction in which the previous work forms the starting point for the next. The finished series is then to be understood as a closed information cycle.
